paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1491-    71	2 Data
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1492-    72	2.1 The ledger
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1493-    73	Scott’s essays disclose giving in dated tranches totaling $26.39 billion nominal over 2020–2025.
paper/review/sol/methodology.log:1494:    74	The model inflates each tranche to 2026 dollars with CPI-U, so dollars and cost-effectiveness
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1495-    75	evidence share one price level: $30.3B total. All derivations below, and the replication repository,
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1496-    76	start from a verbatim snapshot of the Yield Giving gift database retrieved July 11, 2026 (Yield
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-1497-    77	Giving 2026).
