paper/review/sol/methodology.log-2066-   638	model, including the reader who identified the original mispricing of internationally delivered
paper/review/sol/methodology.log:2067:   639	health dollars. The model, audits, and this manuscript were built with Anthropic’s Claude,
paper/review/sol/methodology.log-2068-   640	with additional adversarial review by OpenAI models; all judgments and errors are mine. This
