paper/review/sol/citations.log:81:from $26.39 billion nominal ($30.3B in 2026 dollars), a blended $150,067 per QALY, and a
paper/review/sol/citations.log-82-benefit–cost ratio of 4.9 at the U.S. government’s value per QALY (U.S. Department of Health
